
once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey on a tree, which was on the banks of a river. in the same forest there lived a crockodile and his wife. one day the crockodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree. the kind hearted monkey offered him som fruits. the crockodile came the next day for more fruits as he loved them. As the days passed by the crockodile and the monkey became good friends
